    "Government encouragement policies and financial support have become an important driving force for the development of autonomous vehicles in China.",
    "This paper gives a more comprehensive introduction from the definition of autonomous vehicles, research and development process to the technical application of artificial intelligence in autonomous vehicles, and the global autonomous driving market, and summarizes the research status of key domestic scientists, in order to understand the current development status of China's industry and international competition positioning.",
